            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6277.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from Alphonse de Candolle, 15 July 1868</ref> and n. 3.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6277.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from Alphonse de Candolle, 15 July 1868</ref> and n. 4. In <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> 1: 20, CD referred to the ‘persistence or inheritance’ of the power of moving the scalp muscles.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f4">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6264.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from Alphonse de Candolle, 2 July 1868</ref>, and <ref target="./DCP-LETT-6269.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to Alphonse de Candolle, 6 July 1868</ref>.</note>
